snippet.title: Hoei Space Battle
snippet.description:
best; 10,790
1980 Hoei Sangyo (Coreland Technology/Banpresto)

I put the company's name to avoid confusion with a bootleg of Gingateikoku no Gyakushu/UniWar S, that is also titled "Space Battle".
